dct_title_s: The Electric and International Telegraph Company's map of the telegraph lines of Europe, 1856
dct_description_sm: Cover title: The Electric Telegraph Company's map of Europe. "Messages can be transmitted between all stations named in the margin." Includes insets of southern Scandinavia and northeastern Russia.
dct_publisher_sm: London : published under the authority of the Electric Telegraph Company, by Day & Son, lithrs. ..., 1856.
